$$ PokémonLang Test Program
$$ Prints "hello world" and counts from 1 to 10

Move EmptyBall StartBattle fob fcb OpenBall
    $$ Print hello world
    pikapika fob "hello world" fcb dot

    $$ Declare counter variable
    Pikachu i evo 1 dot

    $$ Count from 1 to 10 and print each number
    AshTrain fob i evo 1 dot i <= 10 dot i evo i atk 1 fcb OpenBall
        pikapika fob i fcb dot
    CloseBall

    back 0 dot
CloseBall
